# File uploading dashboard

## Dashboard to monitor uploading process
Contains 4 counters to display status of uploading files. Solution provides visual status bar with table to display detailed files overview based on selected status.


## Project setup
Clone the project and use the following commands to run it locally:

### Frontend (Vite)

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

---

### Backend (Node)

#### Set `.env` variables
- in `.env`:

```
COSMOS_ENDPOINT=https://<cosmos-account>.documents.azure.com:443/
COSMOS_KEY=<key>
COSMOS_DB=<db-name>
COSMOS_CONTAINER=<container-name>
PORT=8080
```

#### Run

```bash
cd backend
node index.js
```
---


* Backend running on: `http://localhost:8080`
* Frontend running on: `http://localhost:5173`